mindmap
  root((🌟 SUAR Platform
  Architecture & Constraints))

    🏗️ Kiến trúc hệ thống
      🖥️ Client
        Svelte 5 + Inertia.js
        Server-side rendering
      ⚙️ Server
        AdonisJS 7 / TypeScript
        Clean Architecture + DDD
        CQRS Commands + Queries
        Thin Controllers — HTTP adapter only
        Event-driven architecture
      🧩 Layers
        📨 DTO Layer
          Request DTOs — input validation
          Response DTOs — API output shape
        📋 Application Layer — Actions
          Commands — Fetch → Decide → Persist
          Queries — Fetch → Transform → Return
          Application Mapper — DTO ↔ Domain Entity
        🧠 Domain Layer — Business Core
          Domain Entity — business logic, pure TS
          Repository Interface — data access contract
          Domain Mapper — entity ↔ props
          Rules/Policies — pure functions, PolicyResult
        🔌 Infrastructure Layer
          ORM Entity — Lucid model, table mapping
          Repository Impl — implements domain interface
          Infra Mapper — ORM Model ↔ Domain Entity
      🗄️ Data Layer
        PostgreSQL 23 tables, UUIDv7, no FK
        MongoDB 3 collections
         Audit logs, Notifications, Activity logs
        Redis 2 connections
         DB0 Sessions/Locks, DB1 Cache

    🔗 External Systems
      🔐 OAuth
       Google + GitHub
      📡 WebSocket / SSE
       ⚠️ Transmit configured but transport=null
       NOT delivering realtime messages

    ⚠️ Concerns & Constraints
      🛡️ Trust Verification
        3 tiers
         Community 0.5 / Org 0.8 / Partner 1.0
        Credibility score
         0-100 scale
      🕵️ Fraud Detection
        ✅ mutual_high
        ✅ bulk_same_level
        ✅ new_account_high
        ❌ sudden_spike (not implemented)
        ❌ frequency_anomaly (not implemented)
        ❌ ip_collusion (placeholder)
      📏 Business Rules
        Domain Entity methods
        Pure rule functions, 0 DB deps
        PolicyResult pattern
        Testable in isolation
      🗺️ Mapper Flow
        Write: Request DTO → Domain Entity → ORM Entity
        Read: ORM Entity → Domain Entity → Response DTO
